import React from 'react';

const OceanWaveLogo = ({ className }) => {
  return (
    <svg className={className} viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path
        fill="#3B82F6"
        d="M0 0 L50 10 L100 0 L100 100 L0 100 Z"
      />
      <path
        fill="#2563EB"
        d="M0 20 C20 30, 40 30, 50 20 C60 30, 80 30, 100 20 L100 100 L0 100 Z"
      />
      <text
        x="50%"
        y="60%"
        dominantBaseline="middle"
        textAnchor="middle"
        fill="white"
        fontSize="24"
        fontWeight="bold"
      >
        OpsCanvas
      </text>
    </svg>
  );
};

export default OceanWaveLogo;
